00:30:16.030 --> 00:30:17.090
Te salvaré.

00:30:23.550 --> 00:30:24.180
Subirse.

00:30:28.510 --> 00:30:29.090
¿Dónde crees que estás corriendo?

00:30:30.270 --> 00:30:31.660
